title: Cross-Section: a Collection of Short Stories - Conor Engelbrecht
description:
A collection of short stories in a variety of genres, including fantasy, sci-fi and horror. I'm uploading it because I know paying for things sucks and I want as many people as possible to read it.

List of stories:
Four Hours
Maurice
A Prelude
Compacted
Desecration Gardens
The Death of a Day
The Duel
The Rogue Bus
